> Kup and grimlok continued traking Rodimus's signature, after a while 
> they stopped and scanned the area with their optics

Kup and Grimlock are easily able to find the hole in the ground. The ground around the hole is much disturbed, as if something large had made a hole, covered it, then something smaller had dug it out again. There is a hole in the ground, just large enough for a single mech to dig through at a time. If more than one want to go down, they will have to go single file, and be very careful not to collapse the tunnel that has been constructed. 

Legacy drove up to Grimlock and Kup, still in his tank mode, "I WILL ASSIST YOU." 

(TAG: Grimlock, Kup)

Preston
